# JMRI panel XML files go here. Currently empty.
#
# When you build a panel:
#   1. JMRI -> Tools -> Panels -> New Panel -> Layout Editor (or Panel Editor)
#   2. Place sensors, turnouts, signals, blocks as needed.
#   3. JMRI -> File -> Save Panels... -> save as panels/<name>.xml in this folder.
#
# Suggested first panel:
#   shuttle.xml
#     - Schematic of the long track + station with live sensor indicators.
#     - "Start Shuttle" and "Stop Shuttle" buttons that send </START 100> and </KILL ALL>.
#     - Turnout 2 lever wired to the Turnout Table.
